# BMC Project Team Sync

When the user says **"Invoque full team"**, **sync project state**, **actualizar estado del proyecto**, **full team run**, **equipo completo**, or **keep everyone updated** after a change, use the Project Team Sync skill and run the full team.

## Load skill

Read and follow: `.cursor/skills/bmc-project-team-sync/SKILL.md`

## Invoque full team

**Invocación unificada:** "Invoque full team" activa el full team run. Ver `docs/team/INVOQUE-FULL-TEAM.md` para el flujo completo. El Orquestador ejecuta pasos 0–9 e invoca **todos los roles** de `docs/team/PROJECT-TEAM-FULL-COVERAGE.md` **§2** (N = filas vigentes) y **considera §2.2** (skills transversales) en paso 0. Alta de agentes: **§2.3**.

